data: {"generated_at": "2026-05-11T07:23:40.996296+00:00", "nia": {"status": "nia_completed", "source_id": "286018d3-bfb1-44c7-8c14-ca1874385752", "source_name": "Viewlytics TikTok Corpus", "created": false, "prepared_sources": 3, "indexed_files": 3, "query_status": "ok", "answer": "# Viewlytics TikTok Corpus Analysis\n\n## \ud83c\udfaf Strongest Hook Themes\n\n**1. Struggle-to-Success Narrative**\n- \"Don't strive for an EASIER life, work to be a STRONGER person\" (17.52% engagement)\n- \"This is just the beginning\" with #startingover #growingpains (18.47% engagement)\n- Resonates with entrepreneurial journey messaging\n\n**2. Relatable POV/CEO Content**\n- #ynpov #ceo combinations showing high engagement (16.57%)\n- Gen Z workplace humor (#genz #ceo #pov: 10.2% engagement, 42.5M views)\n- Authentic \"day in the life\" perspectives\n\n**3. Motivational/Hopecore**\n- #hopecore #business content (24.54% engagement - highest in corpus)\n- #motivation #success combinations\n- Vision-casting messages (\"Tap into your vision, then charge them to see it\" - 12.88%)\n\n## \ud83d\udc65 Persona Angles\n\n**High-Performing Segments:**\n- **Startup Builders**: Data analysts, engineers, graduates in tech hubs (Seattle, Austin, Dublin)\n- **Creator Operators**: Young professionals with certifications, multi-city presence\n- **Student Trend Scouts**: College/school-aged, roommate situations, trend-aware\n- **Budget Families**: Married/partnered, children, care-focused, housing concerns\n\n**Engagement Sweet Spot**: Young professionals (college/graduate level) in urban centers with entrepreneurial aspirations\n\n## \ud83d\udd25 Trend Words (High-Signal)\n\n**Top Performers:**\n- `entrepreneur/entrepreneurship` - consistent across high-engagement videos\n- `fyp/foryou/foryoupage` - algorithmic amplification tags\n- `trending` - meta-trend awareness\n- `motivation/success` - aspirational content markers\n- `business/smallbusiness` - commercial intent\n- `startup/dropshipping` - specific business models\n- `moneytok/money` - financial content vertical\n\n**Emerging Patterns:**\n- `hopecore` - new motivational subgenre\n- `ynpov` - \"your POV\" narrative format\n- `genz` - generational identity marker\n\n## \u26a0\ufe0f Risk Factors\n\n**1. Noise Term Contamination**\n- High presence of noise terms: `supra`, `xyzabc`, `billionaire`, `pourtoiii`, `kawaii`, `kdrama`\n- These dilute targeting precision and may indicate bot/spam content\n\n**2. Audio/Music Dependency**\n- Multiple references to \"original sound\", \"instrumental\", \"sonido original\"\n- Content may be audio-trend dependent (risky for longevity)\n\n**3. Humor/Meme Volatility**\n- #humor #meme content shows lower engagement (4.23%) despite high views\n- Comedy content has unpredictable performance\n\n**4. Geographic Scatter**\n- Personas span too many markets (Spain, Germany, Australia, Canada, US, Ireland, Netherlands)\n- May indicate unfocused targeting or bot-generated seed lists\n\n**5. Engagement Rate Variance**\n- Range: 4.23% to 24.54%\n- Suggests inconsistent content quality or audience mismatch\n\n## \ud83d\udca1 Actionable Insights\n\n**Do More:**\n- Hopecore + business combinations\n- POV/CEO workplace narratives\n- Struggle-to-success storytelling\n- Target 18-30 professionals in tech/startup ecosystems\n\n**Do Less:**\n- Pure humor/meme plays (lower engagement)\n- Over-reliance on trending sounds\n- Geographic over-diversification\n\n**Watch Out:**\n- Noise term pollution in targeting\n- Audio trend dependency\n- Inconsistent engagement signals", "keyword_sets_source": "nia"}, "sources": {"input_video_name": "scan-stream.mp4", "input_video_size": 1024, "input_video_type": "video/mp4", "input_video_url": null, "input_video_key": null, "tiktok_metadata_files": 0, "transcript_source": "/app/bundled/test.tsv", "persona_source": "/app/bundled/personas_1000.jsonl", "brain_sources": ["/app/bundled/cache/brain_peak_activity_video.json", "/app/bundled/cache/viewer_retention_video.json", "/app/bundled/cache/brain_geometry_nodes_video.json"]}, "model": {"reaction_model": "engagement_concat_mlp", "reaction_labels": ["comment", "like", "share", "follow", "saves", "strong_like", "neutral"], "population_size": 200000, "keyword_sets": 50, "persona_dimensions": ["tech_comfort", "price_sensitivity", "privacy_sensitivity", "eco_consciousness", "health_focus", "social_orientation", "work_focus", "novelty_seeking", "age_fraction", "income_proxy", "education_level", "household_load"]}, "videos": {"count": 0, "top": [], "terms": [{"term": "you're", "count": 2}, {"term": "money", "count": 2}, {"term": "investor", "count": 2}, {"term": "fundraising", "count": 2}, {"term": "recently", "count": 1}, {"term": "raised", "count": 1}, {"term": "million", "count": 1}, {"term": "venture", "count": 1}, {"term": "capital", "count": 1}, {"term": "funding", "count": 1}, {"term": "startup", "count": 1}, {"term": "here's", "count": 1}, {"term": "biggest", "count": 1}, {"term": "learning", "count": 1}, {"term": "advice", "count": 1}, {"term": "ever", "count": 1}, {"term": "having", "count": 1}, {"term": "raise", "count": 1}, {"term": "business", "count": 1}, {"term": "most", "count": 1}, {"term": "critical", "count": 1}, {"term": "thing", "count": 1}, {"term": "think", "count": 1}, {"term": "raising", "count": 1}, {"term": "give", "count": 1}, {"term": "excuse", "count": 1}, {"term": "any", "count": 1}, {"term": "conversation", "count": 1}, {"term": "subconsciously", "count": 1}, {"term": "looking", "count": 1}], "hashtags": []}, "keyword_sets": [{"id": "kw-01", "label": "Creator Operators 1", "keywords": ["spain", "single", "data", "analyst", "child", "certification", "empty", "seattle"], "content_noise_terms": [], "noise_level": 0.012, "persona_count": 4000}, {"id": "kw-02", "label": "Startup Builders 1", "keywords": ["data", "graduate", "chicago", "states", "engineer", "austin", "germany", "certification"], "content_noise_terms": [], "noise_level": 0.018, "persona_cou